From: linuxcnc-node maintainers <maintainers@linuxcnc-node.local>
Date: Tue, 21 Jul 2026 20:00:00 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] Add headless and manpage-free build options

Add an explicit backend-only build mode and make manpage generation
independently optional.  Keep the default GUI and documentation behaviour
unchanged, while allowing minimal images to build without graphical stacks or
Asciidoctor.

